Having provided little to cheer on the pitch, Borussia Dortmund's stars attempted to bring their fans a little happiness another way this week - by serving them beer.

Jurgen Klopp's side sit bottom of the Bundesliga with just 11 points from 13 games, having finished second behind Bayern Munich last season.

Even qualification from their Champions League group, where they lead Arsenal by two points going into the final round of matches, hasn't been enough to lift the gloom around the Westfalenstadion.

